Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the Union Lords are gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the center is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The banner of the Marquis of Jalucia,\NLord Alexis Doucet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and ask the Margrave of Waldlind\Nfor reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dawson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Waldlind is battling\Nthe Altirk Treaty as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can send\Nreinforcements to the center of Alonne.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are now a Lord of the Alliance,\Nso show us some valor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My master, Lord of Dawson, Sir Bernard Durum,\Nis requesting to return allegiance to the Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly request\Nthat you show mercy in your ruling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I deny that request.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he hands over his territories and Crest,\Nand surrenders to me, I will spare his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that insolent Doucet moppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.15,0:01:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll show him how to wage war!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll sally from the castle,\Nand destroy the army surrounding us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we win this battle,\NI will reward the mercenary troops,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and grant the Lords\Nwith new court ranks and territories!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So fight with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So he chose to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me play my music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,While keeping a fixed distance\Nfrom the enemy mercenary troops,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the light cavalry will fire from horseback.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The light crossbow corps\Nwill advance while dispersing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Envelope the Order of Knights\Nas they charge towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gently at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then... faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The right wing is in disarray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back for now, and regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Left wing, spread out further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, gently...\NGently...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is no battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Alexis creating a work of art!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the white flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dawson was defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the Union did us quite the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who was in command of the Union forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Marquis of Jalucia, Sir Alexis Doucet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All the Lords have been lauding\Nthat he led with such flair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has the Lord of Nord been notified?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He already knows, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was laughing and saying that he can't wait\Nto meet the Marquis of Jalucia on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him he shouldn't let his guard down\Nat any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alexis's talents are without peer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if he succeeds to display them\Non the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he will prove to be a formidable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you set foot on the battlefield, Alexis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now you'll get dragged into the war\Nthat's just about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's telling me to watch out\Nfor that Doucet brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've also received word that a massive\NUnion fleet is already headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am known as the Sea King,\Nand he wants to wage a naval battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're mobilizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go annihilate that Doucet moppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jalucia has an ironclad ship in her fleet.\NIt's known as the Invincible Warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once we board those ships,\Nthat iron armor will be utterly useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll seize them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've spotted the Nordic fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy numbering around 1,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ring formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for the enemy to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Union fleet has come to a stop,\Nand appears to be waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll attack in one go! Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of battle formation is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter which ship we board,\Nwe can cross over to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must know nothing about naval battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or if you look at it another way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no matter which ship we board,\Nthey'll get reinforcements from other ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll disperse and surround the enemy fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we assault at the same time\Nfrom all directions,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the enemy can't concentrate their firepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, activate Battle Flag Berserk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy fleet is dispersing as they approach!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, lower your rafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Draw the enemy ships near.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by for further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Flag Telcio, confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've just lost their minds\Nbecause of the battle flag's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll stop moving once they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ironclad, open fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of battle is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing but a siege!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that me, the Sea King,\Nwill fall to those weakling Union Lords?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My King, let's retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should return to Nord,\Nand stage a comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to live in disgrace\Nafter being utterly routed like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this,\NI will continue to fight until I die as a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gods of Valhalla, watch over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My soul shall travel to where you reside,\Nbecome your warrior, and prepare for the twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand your ground! Fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surround him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get near Sir Alexis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Douce...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alexis, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get near Sir Alexis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop attacking!\NBring this monster down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is he immortal or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That warrior is brimming\Nwith insanity and murderous intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can a human turn into such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You damned monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chop its head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This crazed warrior is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's the Sea King Erik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Its massive frame and appearance\Nis unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For this to be his end...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alexis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Chaos Core is almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alexis, please take the Sea King's Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will soon be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that recent battle at sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's fair to say the three forces, the Alliance,\Nthe Union, and the Treaty, are now evenly matched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so we, the Altirk Treaty, propose\Nfor the Alliance to call a truce with the Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A truce is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The loss of the Nordic king is a huge blow,\Nbut the Alliance still has reserve power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to mobilize all my forces, and assault\Nboth the Treaty and the Union into oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll be in formation\Nawaiting your arrival
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,where the Union and the Alliance\Npreviously had their final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should the Alliance win,\Nwe'll hand over our Crests and territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But in the event that there's no clear winner,\Nwe'd like you to accept our proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really need to give you my promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. But a three-way struggle between\Nall our forces is far from ideal to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think we would only be giving the edge\Nto our true enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The true enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I have any definitive proof,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I believe it was the Mage Academy\Nthat set off the Great Hall Tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not your guess is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,once this battle is decided,\NI'm certain it will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind telling me one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say to Alexis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the Marquis of Jalucia\Nsuddenly decide to take action?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must've realized\Nit's what he needed to do for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you unified the Crests by military force,\Nit would be you who got hurt in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've made so many sacrifices\Nin order to walk down this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot stop in my tracks now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo intends to try to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Sir Alexis must have also\Nsteeled his resolve to do so as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aubest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to gather all the Alliance Lords\Nand have a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to advocate war\Nagainst the Treaty and the Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds somewhat impetuous...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The final battle will be held not far from Eramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of the Lords will gather there\Nfrom across the Continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the outcome of the battle,\Nwe might see the creation of the Grancrest.
